Name: Absolver Captain's Seal
AttributesDescription:
After casting Resonance Liberation, increases Basic Attack Crit. DMG of all Resonators in the team by 40% for 15s and reduces their Resonance Skill cooldown by 10s.

This Token can be used up to 2 times in Whimpering Wastes.
BgDescription: A ship of the Order Tribunal, often found cruising the sea. It always arrives in time to "mediate" conflicts. They may have "absolved" the guilty, but others never "absolve" them.
ObtainedShowDescription: After casting Resonance Liberation, increases all team members' Critical Basic Attack DMG by 40% for 15s and reduces their Resonance Skill cooldown by 10s.
